    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While the exterior paint still holds a nice shine, you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. It is a reliable, honest car that is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate repairs.",
